<p align="center">***************<br />
    <strong>Teacher Workshop</strong></p>
<p>Accompanying teachers, parents, and other adult student  supervisors have the opportunity to participate in a &ldquo;hands-on&rdquo; workshop and  informational session on a variety of topics. The keynote speaker will also be  available for questions and answers.</p>
<p>Please be sure to fill out the <strong><em>EYH08 Teacher Workshop  Registration Form</em></strong> either online or fax it in together with the student  registrations.</p>
